### Create store
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/stores/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "owner_id": 1,
  "name": "My Store",
  "description": "A sample store",
  "contact_info": "123-456-7890",
  "delivery_fee": 100,
  "image_url": "https://example.com/image.png",
  "store_code": "STORE001",
  "is_active": true,
  "is_verified": false,
  "rating": 0,
  "total_reviews": 0,
  "area": "Downtown",
