### Get store by owner ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/stores/owner/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get all stores
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/stores/all
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get unverified stores
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/stores/unverified-stores
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get stores by location
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/stores/location/Cityville?state=Countyshire
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Rate a store
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/stores/rate/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "rating": 5
}

### Verify a store
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/stores/verify/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get store by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/stores/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Update a store
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/stores/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "description": "Updated store description",
  "is_active": true
}

### Delete a store
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/stores/1
